{"tid":793014,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星 大快活塊雞胸真係好撚正","createTime":"2018-08-25T04:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T06:37:22.000Z","uid":20362,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"667e280b11c4dc0b72334027d8d7dedf74bad662","tid":793014,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"食落成塊雞排咁 又淋又冇腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經走汁 真係有雞味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時百佳買果啲假雞胸 陣味臭撚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個飯真係食到想嘔 濕撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知係咪我呢間手勢唔好 好彩有塊雞胸中和返<br />\n單係呢塊雞胸就足以令大快活成為三大快餐店之首<br />\n應該要勒令大快活公開雞胸既煮法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令佢作為香港既非物質文化遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a0ab3e4ea28f373025baae52ee5054cd1b43bc","tid":793014,"uid":33359,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"自從食過百里香之後就無食過大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3644e29c3b4043f42930ac8855d86bd562a19d1c","tid":793014,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"負評咩意思<br />\n係咪未試過白焯雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"81e09489540b71708c8302ab91b1e0c72936753f","tid":793014,"uid":189336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f88922a414ce7feb8bc94329dde7bff812eb7cd3","tid":793014,"uid":203